另一方面，[[古老地球创造论|古老地球创造论]]（{{lang|en|Old Earth creationism}}）则相信，圣经中提到的六天创世与认为宇宙有十亿年历史的科学共识能够和谐共处。根据诗篇（{{CUV|诗篇|90|4}}）、彼得后书（{{CUV|彼得后书|3|8}}），时间“一日如千年，千年如一日”。如果1000这个数字被阐释为另一个任意大的数字，正如文中暗示的，那么地球的实际年龄就变成了一个科学的事物，而非宗教辩论。然而，这不是唯一的阐释，古老地球创造论学者休·罗斯把创世六天的每一天都看作是很长的实际，这样做是由于希伯来语词汇{{rtl-lang|he|yom}}具有多种释义以及其他关于创世的圣经章节。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.reasons.org/interpreting-genesis/other-creation-passages/response-genesis-and-big-bang |author=Ross, Hugh |coauthors=Endara, Miguel |title=Response to Genesis and the Big Bang by Gerald Schroeder |publisher=Reasons To Believe |date=31 Dec 1990 |accessdate=2012-01-28 |archive-date=2011-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927013648/http://www.reasons.org/interpreting-genesis/other-creation-passages/response-genesis-and-big-bang |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.christian-knowledge.com/forums/genesis-chapter1/day-genesis-t8.html |author=Russell, Ryan |title=Day 1 (Genesis 1:1-5) |publisher=Christian Knowledge |work=Genesis: verse-by-verse Bible Study |accessdate=3 Dec 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120724071849/http://www.christian-knowledge.com/forums/genesis-chapter1/day-genesis-t8.html |archivedate=2012-07-24 }}</ref>

